headline: Deere & Company (DE): A Bull Case Theory
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on Deere & Company on Max Dividends’s Substack by Max Dividends and Serhio MaxDividends. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on DE. Deere & Company’s share was trading at $500.98 as of August 1st. DE’s trailing and forward P/E were 24.20 and 22.08, respectively according to Yahoo Finance. […]
